{{!< default}}

{{#contentFor 'htmlLang'}}{{@site.locale}}{{/contentFor}}

{{#contentFor 'styles'}}
    <link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='{{asset 'css/plans.css'}}' />
{{/contentFor}}

{{#contentFor 'title'}}Premium Membership - {{meta_title}}{{/contentFor}}

{{#contentFor 'meta'}}
<meta
    name="description"
    content="{{@site.title}} is a premium publication about coding, tech world,
            entrepreneurship, remote work and the life of a mordern
            developer. Members get access to weekly new content and a
            monthly newsletter. Prices and plans are listed below."
/>
{{/contentFor}}

<div class='mds-plans'>
    <div class='mds-container'>
        <header class='mds-header'>
            <h1 class='mds-title'>Mindsers' Blog Premium Membership</h1>
            <p>
                {{@site.title}} is a premium publication about coding, tech world,
                entrepreneurship, remote work and the life of a mordern
                developer.
                </p><p>
                I write free tech content to help developer from all levels to improve themself.
                But other kind of content are available on this blog too: if you're like me
                and love the remote life, the coffee ceremonial or building businesses, this premium subscription is for you!
            </p>
        </header>
    </div>

    <section class='mds-plan-grid'>
        <div class='mds-container'>
            <div class='plan-container'>
                <div class='plan-bg'>
                    <header>
                        <h2>Free signup</h2>
                    </header>
                    <section class='plan-body'>
                        <ul>
                            <li>📗 Get complete access to the public blog
                                posts library</li>
                            <li>📫 Receive an email notification for new public blog posts</li>
                            <li>👥 Get access to our discord community</li>
                            <li>🚫 No advertising</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>
                    <section class='plan-price'>
                        <a href='/signup/' class='button highlighted'>$0</a>
                        <p class="notices">No spam ever. Unsubscribe in a single click at any time.</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='plan-container'>
                <div class='plan-bg'>
                    <header>
                        <h2>Yearly Subscription</h2>
                    </header>
                    <section class='plan-body'>
                        <ul>
                            <li>📚 Get complete access to the entire blog
                                posts library (including premium post)</li>
                            <li>📫 Receive en email notification when a new
                                blog post is published</li>
                            <li>🎭 Get access to exclusive additional contents</li>
                            <li>👥 Get access to our discord community</li>
                            <li>💼 Get VIP answers to your questions</li>
                            <li>🎙 Get access to the comments and discussion section on posts</li>
                            <li>💌 Receive the monthly {{@site.title}}'s newsletter</li>
                            <li>✊🏽 Support an independent publication</li>
                            <li>🚫 No advertising</li>
                            <li class='eco'><strong>♻️ We give back 1.5% of your subscription</strong>
                                to help removing CO₂ from the
                                atmosphere.</li>
                            <li><strong>⚡️ Pay 1 quick payment instead of 12!</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>💸 Get an extra 17% discount</strong></li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>
                    <section class='plan-price'>
                        <a
                            href='javascript:'
                            data-members-plan='Yearly'
                            class='button highlighted'
                        >{{price @price.yearly}} / year</a>
                        <p class="notices">No spam ever. Unsubscribe in a single click at any time.</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
                <div class='plan-favourite-notice'>
                    <div class='arrow'>
                        <div class='curve'></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class='notice'>
                        My favourite readers’ option
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='plan-container'>
                <div class='plan-bg'>
                    <header>
                        <h2>Monthly Subscription</h2>
                    </header>
                    <section class='plan-body'>
                        <ul>
                            <li>📚 Get complete access to the entire blog
                                posts library (including premium post)</li>
                            <li>📫 Receive en email notification when a new
                                blog post is published</li>
                            <li>🎭 Get access to exclusive additional contents</li>
                            <li>👥 Get access to our discord community</li>
                            <li>💼 Get VIP answers to your questions</li>
                            <li>🎙 Get access to the comments and discussion section on posts</li>
                            <li>💌 Receive the monthly {{@site.title}}'s newsletter</li>
                            <li>✊🏽 Support an independent publication</li>
                            <li>🚫 No advertising</li>
                            <li class='eco'><strong>♻️ We give back 1.5% of your subscription</strong>
                                to help removing CO₂ from the
                                atmosphere.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>
                    <section class='plan-price'>
                        <a
                            href='javascript:'
                            data-members-plan='Monthly'
                            class='button highlighted'
                        >{{price @price.monthly}} / month</a>
                        <p class="notices">No spam ever. Unsubscribe in a single click at any time.</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class='mds-patreon'>
        <div class='mds-container'>
            <p>
                Patreon supporters can get full access to the premium content
                depending on their Patreon tier.<br />
                You only have to login using the same address as your Patreon
                account.
            </p>
            <p>
                If the plans listed here aren't convenient for you,<br />
                you can support our independent publication using Patreon and
                giving whatever you want.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a
                    href='https://www.patreon.com/mindsers'
                    class='button patreon'
                    target='_blank'
                    rel='nofollow noreferrer'
                >Support on Patreon</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mds-testimonials">
        <div class="mds-container">
            {{> "testimonials"
                text="I discovered Mindsers on Instagram, and I learned so much since I read his blog (thanks for the C & PHP articles!). The community is the perfect environment to learn new things, come join us !"
                people="Arthur M."
            }}
            {{> "testimonials"
                text="Mindsers' blog is the perfect place to start when learning how to code! Full of good resources and advice."
                people="Maëva C."
            }}
            {{> "testimonials"
                text="Thanks for the blog, there are a lot of great content. I completely agree with what I read here especially in the ＂ Best Practices ＂ section. Keep the good work!"
                people="Yexan"
            }}
            {{> "testimonials"
                text="Super blog de Nath ! Les articles sont bien rédigés et illustrés. Rapides à lire, ils m’ont beaucoup aidé à démystifier certains sujets qui sont abstraits pour les débutants. Les exemples choisis sont pratiques et expliqués simplement. Je recommande à 100 %."
                people="Valérie A."
            }}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class='mds-eco'>
        <div class='mds-container'>
            <p>
                Our goal at Mindsers Blog is to act positively on coders’ life
                but we want to act positively on our planet’s life too.<br />
                Using Stripe Climate we contribute 1.5% of each premium
                subscription to help scale emerging carbon removal technologies.<br
                />
            </p>
            <p>
                <a
                    href='https://stripe.com/climate'
                    class='button secondary'
                    target='_blank'
                    rel='nofollow noreferrer'
                >Learn more about Stripe Climate</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class='mds-faq'>
        <div class='mds-container'>
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

            <div class='mds-faq-grid'>
                <div>
                    <h3>Will I be able to change or cancel my plan?</h3>
                    <p>
                        Premium plans are paid monthly or yearly, and can be
                        updated, changed, or cancelled any time by logging into
                        your account and clicking a button. No contracts, no
                        nonsense.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>I still have questions, how can I contact you?</h3>
                    <p>
                        If you need something else, you can reach out by sending
                        an email to
                        <a
                            href='mailto:hello@mindsers.blog'
                            title='Contact support team'
                            rel='nofollow noreferrer'
                        >hello@mindsers.blog</a>, or message
                        <a
                            href='https://twitter.com/MindsersCodes'
                            title='Twitter'
                            target='_blank'
                            rel='nofollow noreferrer'
                        >@MindsersCodes</a>
                        — and I'll do my best to get back to you as soon as
                        possible.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>How many emails will I get?</h3>
                    <p>
                        A maximum of 2 notification emails per week for the blog
                        posts. You'll also get one email per month for the
                        newsletter.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Do I have to pay twice for the newsletter and the
                        private blog posts?</h3>
                    <p>
                        No, the premium membership contains the newsletter
                        issues and the full blog posts library. You do
                        <strong>not</strong>
                        have to pay twice.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>What are the topics of the posts?</h3>
                    <p>
                        Even if the public blog posts are focused on coding, I
                        share a lot on other topics in the private ones
                        (business, entrepreneurship, social sciences, ethic,
                        etc.).
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Are there other ways to support your work?</h3>
                    <p>
                        Yes. If you only want to donate to support my work you
                        can look at
                        <a
                            href='https://nathanaelcherrier.dev/fr/support/'
                        >nathanaelcherrier.dev/en/support/</a>
                        but only Patreon will give you access to the blog
                        membership. Otherwise the default subscription is
                        provided and secured by Stripe.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
